name: Daefrom
description: DAEFROM technology stack can benefit in any use cases that demand security and decentralization as open finance, personal identification, gaming, sensitive data and many others. DAEFROM network runs a proof-of-work (PoW) consensus protocol. DAEFROM Society, a new social network site built on the DAEFROM blockchain, will launch till 1 year. Using blockchain technology, users will have more control over their data and privacy and the ability to earn free DAEFROM tokens by watching ads and so on.
